            </ul>
        </nav>
    </div>
    <!---HIER KOMMT DIE WEBSITE HIN-->
    <div id="section1">
        <div id="section1_content">
            <h1>GuessMaster</h1>
            <p>Test your general knowlegede with GuessMaster and have fun competing against your friends. Start playing now:</p>
            <a onmouseover="cursorBig()" onmouseout="cursorSmall()" href="#">Play Now</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="section2">
        <h1>GAME IDEA</h1>
        <hr>
        <div id="section2_content">
            <div id="sec2_question">
                <h1>How many People live in Germany?</h1>
                <h2>Your Answer: <span id="writer"><span class="txt-type" data-wait="3000"
                    data-words='["80.000.000 ", "15 ", "I dont know... "]'></span></span></h2>
            </div>
            <div id="sec2_info">
                <ul>
                    <li>Test your general knowledge by answering Questions</li>
                    <li>Speed maters: Try to answer as fast as possible</li>
                    <li>Make fun about stupid friends, that dont know any shit</li>
                    <li>Browser Game: So you dont have to worry about installation or updates</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <h4>GuessMaster</h4>
        <h1>OUR GOAL</h1>
        <p>By developing GuessMaster we have tried to create a simple and fun game that will test your general knowledge and be interesting at the same time. In addition, we try to arrange the game in such a way that the largest possible group is addressed.</p>
    </div>
    <div id="section3">
        <h4>Global</h4>
        <h1>PLAYER STATS</h1>
        <div id="section3_content">
            <div class="sec3_box">
              <img src="/Main/src/MainImages/gameround.png">
              <span class="sec3_data" data-val="400">000</span>
              <span class="sec3_datatext">Played Rounds</span>
            </div>
            <div class="sec3_box">
                <img src="/Main/src/MainImages/correct.png">
              <span class="sec3_data" data-val="340">000</span>
              <span class="sec3_datatext">Correct Answers</span>
            </div>
            <div class="sec3_box">
                <img src="/Main/src/MainImages/user.png">
              <span class="sec3_data" data-val="225">000</span>
              <span class="sec3_datatext">Active Players</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <p>Möchtest du deine persöhnlichen Spielerstatistiken einsehen? <br> Klicke hier und erhalte alle deine eigenen Spielerdaten</p>
        <a onmouseover="cursorBig()" onmouseout="cursorSmall()" href="#">My Playerstats</a>
    </div>
    <div id="section4">

    </div>
